<body>
    <h1>Task 18 - RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"d4e12ef1aa75" id=3D"Task18-RAD-1.Introduction">1. I=
ntroduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"7af8393dd95d" id=3D"Task18-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f1ca8fcb655c">The purpose of this document is to define the =
requirements for deploying multiple websites using <strong>Nginx, AWS Appli=
cation Load Balancer (ALB), SSL, and Route 53 DNS</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"19f080b4a172">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8a2a6a1381b7">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7aaa20105faf">Cloud Engineers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"21283bcf2145">Project Evaluators</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"44e067b2d849">Students and Interns</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"264f10bc905c" id=3D"Task18-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"08ad4252b439"><strong>Included in scope:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d981519608b8">Hosting websites on Nginx EC2</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"bed2470e1546">Hosting websites via Load Balancer</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"83f37d0d025b">Configuring SSL using ACM</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dcf5e996b25d">DNS setup using Route 53</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e95e003224b8">Validation of website access</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1a09dce8bfd0"><strong>Not included:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8fb343f42526">CI/CD pipelines</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3499a2cf962e">Advanced monitoring setup</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c31a78186390">Auto-scaling configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"81a989603c97" id=3D"Task18-RAD-1.3Definitions,Acronyms,andA=
bbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a=
6eaf8e8-2d96-4a39-86d3-e1e8a1493a42" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5f98d5a7bd22">Term</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"cb120b525ea7">Meaning</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"22875f5f76a0">EC2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"06299f9010bc">Elastic Compute Cloud</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1cd87af87a4b">ALB</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"93ee571adcdf">Application Load Balancer</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c526355b7e14">ACM</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"74787f569947">AWS Certificate Manager</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c7b59ae5fa7e">DNS</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b33d81c40a77">Domain Name System</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"99356e6ee875">HTTPS</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1216b8df98eb">Secure HTTP protocol</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0b30c82ce075">Nginx</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d933dc87c237">Web server software</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"6bde276a7181" id=3D"Task18-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8cda7846f420">AWS EC2 Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b98d113a1d03">AWS ALB Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6b6e79ee4470">AWS Route 53 Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"732d87d1b57b">AWS ACM Documentation</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8c16b70a7270">GitHub Repo: hello-world-flask</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"859a2cae3669" id=3D"Task18-RAD-1.5Overview">1.5 Overview</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"60590056b480">This document covers:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0d4ca672d2d1">Architecture design</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d33d9d310e51">Functional requirements</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3e9abbeacf3d">Deployment steps</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d475098f3bd5">Security and performance requirements</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cffacbf1abea">Risk analysis</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"3c9236c5fab1" id=3D"Task18-RAD-2.ProjectOverview">2. Projec=
t Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"d4736abf2732" id=3D"Task18-RAD-2.1ProjectObjectives">2.1 Pr=
oject Objectives</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"42af3f80af6a">Deploy multiple websites using Nginx and ALB</=
p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"da512c670644">Configure DNS routing using Route 53</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ccb3d22e222c">Enable HTTPS using SSL certificates</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f2088c2b4208">Ensure proper traffic routing and load balanci=
ng</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"55c6f7e124ac">Validate correct website delivery</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"54addafc398c" id=3D"Task18-RAD-2.2BusinessGoals">2.2 Busine=
ss Goals</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ac8a0cdc59b5">Learn traffic distribution using ALB</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b09753a3243e">Improve website availability</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"32236f2b12e3">Secure websites using HTTPS</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2635024e152e">Enable domain-based routing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6478ab15fa77">Simulate real-world hosting environment</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"e1b8e38be5ea" id=3D"Task18-RAD-2.3Background">2.3 Backgroun=
d</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6b3782722a22">ABC Technologies wants to test hosting multipl=
e websites using AWS services.</p>
<p local-id=3D"afa4873f4e35">Traditional hosting on a single server has lim=
itations:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"80eeef2bbe1c">No load balancing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3b33f3596a64">No scalability</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"462e11ff90e7">Limited security</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b4bad8694819">This project introduces:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"06ab55a0e140">Nginx for direct hosting</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9996fe088658">ALB for load balancing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"81eeea2190f2">Route 53 for DNS routing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"823fbe0f54e6">ACM for SSL security</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"447940802576" id=3D"Task18-RAD-2.4Constraints">2.4 Constrai=
nts</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8443fb8c289b">Limited AWS resources (free tier)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2267c84c157b">Domain availability required</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7a96b3906267">SSL setup depends on domain validation</p></li=
>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fa0eb1e4c8d0">Manual configuration complexity</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"f94612edfc85" id=3D"Task18-RAD-3.FunctionalRequirements">3.=
 Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"9631eb5ce856" id=3D"Task18-RAD-3.1UseCaseDiagram">3.1 Use C=
ase Diagram</h2><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-cente=
r-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedde=
d-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260321-202632.png" width=3D"468" loadi=
ng=3D"lazy" src=3D"3acc11dbbdc8f0b8ca8495e768f700dc3e67c721a473a32109fd9c68=
6806ae1e" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/atta=
chments/1886388225/image-20260321-202632.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDa=
te=3D1774124801972&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"2164" =
data-width=3D"4164" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resourc=
e-id=3D"1885700367" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource=
-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260321-2=
02632.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-=
resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"18=
86388225" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"2" data-media-id=3D"297=
b4cd7-9efd-4e2c-b228-03b2e0c707d2" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"243">=
</span>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"fdf55a929e61" id=3D"Task18-RAD-3.2UseCases">3.2 Use Cases</=
h2>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"5f5cd739780d" id=3D"Task18-RAD-3.2.1UseCase1:HostWebsiteson=
Nginx(Site1&amp;Site2)">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Host Websites on Nginx (Site 1 &a=
mp; Site 2)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"925ac9250158"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Deploy two websites on a single EC2 instance using Nginx server blocks.</p>
<p local-id=3D"725e2232a58f"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a2ead9f21901">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9938ad9b263e"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0d0f33deb9e7">EC2 instance running</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"995cc3dd843b">Nginx installed</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6d696d4f21ba"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4b7cf5d165e9">Site 1 and Site 2 accessible independently</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5545a79079ad"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b020b06714bc">Install Nginx</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1be6bbadf0ec">Clone GitHub project</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d0fed3d2a999">Modify content for Site 1 and Site 2</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4836ffe464c2">Create server blocks</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2423e627e5ab">Restart Nginx</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"495ebcaafa00"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"db22d3f362fd">Misconfigured server block =E2=86=92 site not =
accessible</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"4e3001827e00" id=3D"Task18-RAD-3.2.2UseCase2:DeployLoadBala=
ncedWebsites(Site3&amp;Site4)">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Deploy Load Balanced Websi=
tes (Site 3 &amp; Site 4)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"18ff2c1e3aac"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Deploy websites across multiple EC2 instances and distribute traffic.</p>
<p local-id=3D"513bffbff644"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e9b0791f2bf1">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"464a56f8ffd5"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"55351c237506">EC2 instances created</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7fe5929e6e95"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4ecb6f615560">Traffic distributed between servers</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e7753ad21b98"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d75f467634a1">Launch 2 EC2 instances</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"aff8ef029f92">Deploy application on both</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ef493ace9450">Modify content (Site 3, Site 4)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2af9f33838a8">Create target group</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"405f9e2fe6b3">Attach instances to ALB</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"77f2d049f0ec"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ef52929aeff2">Instance unhealthy =E2=86=92 removed from ALB<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"6f21a7a1b415" id=3D"Task18-RAD-3.2.3UseCase3:ConfigureSSLus=
ingACM">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Configure SSL using ACM</h3>
<p local-id=3D"3f6327c1b046"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Enable HTTPS for all websites.</p>
<p local-id=3D"20883c6ff5e9"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6640b4ab4d46">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4a40db8e7dc4"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"eb922e0b7eb2">Domain available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7f41a2eceda4"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7f490f00a457">Secure HTTPS connection established</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8ce22f4313f2"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"609671db7f37">Request certificate in ACM</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3a5185d40ed4">Validate domain</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"da996ffcf9f6">Attach certificate to ALB</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dcf55ba38032">Configure HTTPS listener</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3c8c78ea8a07">Redirect HTTP to HTTPS</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"c8219718f5dc"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"85e9e2c8cb99">Validation failure =E2=86=92 certificate not i=
ssued</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"1eb449e93703" id=3D"Task18-RAD-3.2.4UseCase4:ConfigureRoute=
53DNS">3.2.4 Use Case 4: Configure Route 53 DNS</h3>
<p local-id=3D"2595f32254d3"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Map domain names to EC2 and ALB.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f82c0d033df6"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5428bbd5cc82">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"469b732a59cb"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"91460c6c37e6">Hosted zone created</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d8908d463bfc"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1cca36fd6f49">Domains resolve correctly</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"960284265731"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b31c9c2ae957">Create hosted zone</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b952c52e7a51">Add A records</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8e9bedea830a">Map domains to EC2/ALB</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"38526160944a">Save configuration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5be923c4d4ae">Verify DNS resolution</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"795c5133723f"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"39bf01404d96">Incorrect mapping =E2=86=92 wrong site loads</=
p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 local-id=3D"d2cb9da30fc5" id=3D"Task18-RAD-3.2.5UseCase5:ValidateWebsit=
eAccess">3.2.5 Use Case 5: Validate Website Access</h3>
<p local-id=3D"0abd5abaf611"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Ensure all websites are working correctly.</p>
<p local-id=3D"44aa79ccd481"><strong>Actors:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"17ff4cca6951">Test User</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"13f6eba25abd"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c8f5f3de8ef0">Deployment completed</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d7d754753ba7"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cf37618ec7b0">All sites accessible via HTTPS</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2d68fd2bd9a9"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4eb18c6463c7">Open domain in browser</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a716ac190f19">Check HTTPS connection</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a6075611121c">Verify content</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8d365e44d2ed">Test load balancing</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9952a0c904aa">Confirm routing</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"3802133c5f06"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"294b494aff82">Wrong content =E2=86=92 configuration issue</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"46ed353d625f" id=3D"Task18-RAD-4.Non-FunctionalRequirements=
">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"5280f468d907" id=3D"Task18-RAD-4.1PerformanceRequirements">=
4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"500b025eda51">Fast response time (&lt;2 seconds)</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"347a41495d9a">Load balancing ensures performance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5cbd44cb4ed6">Efficient DNS resolution</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"4f2cfde5080c" id=3D"Task18-RAD-4.2SecurityRequirements">4.2=
 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c8446f2d9697">HTTPS enabled using SSL</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a0e10520076b">Secure communication via ALB</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d0dbc9aa69c8">Restricted access to EC2</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"7b64ec3a8898" id=3D"Task18-RAD-4.3UsabilityRequirements">4.=
3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2b06a1b8eb15">Easy domain-based access</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9450dff8c2b8">Clear website identification</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"24108ed67b3f">Simple configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"caa8583a2308" id=3D"Task18-RAD-4.4ReliabilityRequirements">=
4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"755f537ca362">ALB ensures high availability</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5a89335254c1">Multiple EC2 instances reduce downtime</p></li=
>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c581656eb66b">SSL ensures secure connection</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"4f26f4a043ee" id=3D"Task18-RAD-4.5ComplianceRequirements">4=
.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f4013f1adce0">Follow AWS best practices</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f08d253de168">Secure data transmission</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"773c87ec9801">Proper domain validation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"e6f2dc8e341f" id=3D"Task18-RAD-5.AssumptionsandDependencies=
">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"db673bae7666" id=3D"Task18-RAD-5.1Assumptions">5.1 Assumpti=
ons</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"555fbad279a5">Domain name is available</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"acf4e93aa5a9">AWS services are accessible</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3386ff800258">GitHub repository is working</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"0de2146b89ba" id=3D"Task18-RAD-5.2Dependencies">5.2 Depende=
ncies</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"118a993f419d">AWS EC2</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"1c74f50b9ca8">AWS ALB</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b3f00b6d1df9">AWS Route 53</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f1b915a2051a">AWS ACM</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a77c2ce580fa">Nginx</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"06acecc36b08" id=3D"Task18-RAD-6.RiskAnalysis">6. Risk Anal=
ysis</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"e4bdc5d7b217" id=3D"Task18-RAD-6.1RiskIdentification">6.1 R=
isk Identification</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6ae3e4bdc3c1">SSL certificate validation failure</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a27ba86393c8">DNS misconfiguration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"31ef03e4f568">Nginx misconfiguration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cc092e5236a6">ALB health check failure</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"111b807a476a" id=3D"Task18-RAD-6.2RiskMitigation">6.2 Risk =
Mitigation</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"24c99258a3f0">Verify DNS before SSL</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"291260c515ec">Test configurations step-by-step</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2ab6f6bd30b1">Monitor ALB health checks</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8103a50815b2">Use logs for debugging</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
